channel.title: Help Please, 100 Errors
channel.description:
Im About To Die Here.... Im Using Fr33sc4p3 Source.. And I Recently Added A Desert Area (Which I Don't Recommend To Anyone, EVER) And It Had WAY To Many Bugs, So I Took It Off. Now Im Getting 100 Errors When I Compile, And Only Acouple Are Related To Where That Coding Used To Be. Im Getting Abunch About Bank Coding, And Abunch About Addobject, And Then Lots More About Other Random Things. The Only Thing That MIGHT Have To Do With The Coding I Added, Was In Addobject, But I Looked Them Over, And There All Fine. And The Rest Of The Coding Looks Fine Too.. I Just Don't Know What To Do.... I Can't Start Over With A New Source.. Thats A Waste Of My Time... Please, PLEASE, Somone Help Me.
-Will
